headline: Totino’s™ Unveils Next-Level Indulgence with New Totino’s Ultimate Pizza
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, July 23, 2025--Say goodbye to boring snacks and lunchtime slumps – Totino’s™ is leveling up the flavor with its boldest launch yet, Totino’s Ultimate, a new offering made for pizza lovers and unapologetic cravings. The lineup kicks off with a brand-new premium product: Totino's Ultimate Pizza crafted to deliver delicious flavor and satisfying bites.

headline: New Progresso® Pitmaster Soups Take on Grilling Season – Without the Grill
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, July 23, 2025--Fire up your appetite, not your grill. This summer, Progresso® is bringing the unmistakable taste of a backyard cookout to your kitchen with the launch of Progresso Pitmaster, a bold new line of BBQ-inspired soups packed with juicy, delicious meats, roasted vegetables and 14g of protein or more per can.
